{"tid":1696590,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"慢鏡發現何妖被插2大疑點","createTime":"2019-11-06T09:06:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T09:46:24.000Z","uid":266584,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"438b7a723ec8d63310d93a4af0b0e3deb67f66d5","tid":1696590,"uid":266584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:06:06.000Z","msg":"慢鏡發現何妖被插2大疑點，1.留意畫面左邊白背心係刀手打開袋時出現準備動作，出刀後佢係第一個有反應；2.刀手以極速刺向何妖胸口前就停左，等何妖做擋格動作，留意係刀停左何妖先做到反應，冇超慢鏡係知睇唔到把刀停左。只要睇番正常速度播放就知出手咁快，距離咁近，又咁突然係擋唔到。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/qy2pm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fqy2pm&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX4MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=37c2f03e\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/qy2pm</a>"},{"pid":"d09e8af7b418c5fc5f2587b5dfc70007dcf8b39b","tid":1696590,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:06:33.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，推post &amp; 借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n******眾籌*******<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先45%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX4MY%2B